<br>
Some of the Gods have declared war upon the amazons.  They dare push their selves upon us that we should submit.  This shall not happen.  I, Hippolyte, daughter of Otere, do call upon my athelfi to join me in battle against these forces.<br>
<br>
Amazons Unite!<br>
Hippolyte<br>
<br>
<br>
